### 1. 管理员登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
    client.global.set("authHeader", "Bearer " + response.body.token);
%}

### 2. 获取统计数据
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/stats
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 3. 获取用户列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 4. 更新用户（需要替换 {id} 为实际用户ID）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/8
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updated_user",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 5. 删除用户（需要替换 {id} 为实际用户ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/8
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 6. 获取知识库列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/knowledge
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 7. 新增知识库
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/knowledge
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "常见诈骗类型",
  "content": "这是关于常见诈骗类型的详细说明...",
  "category": "防骗知识"
}

### 8. 删除知识库（需要替换 {id} 为实际知识库ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/knowledge/1
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 9. 获取案例列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/cases
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 10. 新增案例（已修正字段名）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/cases
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "网络购物诈骗案例",
  "content": "某用户在网上购物时遭遇诈骗，损失了5000元...",
  "category": "网络诈骗",
  "fraudType": "购物诈骗",
  "victimInfo": "30岁，北京",
  "warningTips": "警惕低价诱惑，选择正规平台"
}

### 11. 删除案例（需要替换 {id} 为实际案例ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/cases/1
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 12. 获取帖子列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/posts
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 13. 删除帖子（需要替换 {id} 为实际帖子ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/posts/1
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 14. 获取举报列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/reports
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

### 15. 更新举报状态（需要替换 {id} 为实际举报ID）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/reports/1/status
Authorization: {{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "RESOLVED"
}